Name: Average resolution time following 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Median duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Longest duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to any activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x0000029E3FC4F910> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to any activity excluding 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of all 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration between 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Duration variance of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total count of transitions from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to any other activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Duration from first 'Unmatched + Unmatched' occurrence to last 'Unmatched + Unmatched' occurrence in the log
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
